{"tid":756334,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"“天津飯”在日本知名   中國人卻沒聽過？","createTime":"2018-07-26T03:19:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-26T16:25:23.000Z","uid":184679,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"b790c5735ddd0f7abfa1bedb224c74a839dccbc3","tid":756334,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T03:19:45.000Z","msg":"日媒稱，東京有很多有名的煎餃店，總是人滿為患，備受歡迎。不用說，煎餃是從中國傳到日本的，但日本還有一些自主發展起來的獨特&ldquo;中餐&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n　　據《日本經濟新聞》網站7月24日報道，日本人認為有些食物是中餐館的必備菜品，不會感到不可思議，但從中國人的角度來看，似乎會感覺&ldquo;竟然有這樣的中餐？&rdquo;其代表性案例就是天津飯（或稱天津蓋飯），這是種很著名的食品，在日本的中餐館裡，沒有天津飯的店鋪很少。<br />\n<br />\n　　報道稱，天津飯是指在米飯上蓋上芙蓉蟹和芙蓉蛋，然後再在上面澆上酸甜的芡汁。具體製作方法是，在攪勻的蛋液中加入蟹、蝦、葱和香菇等配料之後炒熟，蓋在米飯上，再在上面澆上芡汁即可。在日本的中餐館裡，天津飯的價格很便宜。日本東部主要用番茄醬勾芡，日本西部則用醬油和鹽勾芡。<br />\n<br />\n　　關於天津飯的起源，主要有兩種說法。一種說法是1910年，東京淺草的中餐館&ldquo;來來軒&rdquo;的廚師被客人要求&ldquo;快點做出能吃的東西&rdquo;，於是廚師利用手頭的雞蛋和螃蟹製作出了芙蓉蟹，然後將其蓋到米飯上。但至於為什麼命名時加上天津二字，沒有人知道。<br />\n<br />\n　　另一個說法是，同樣在大正時代，大阪一家名為&ldquo;大正軒&rdquo;的中餐館的廚師利用天津盛產的梭子蟹製作出芙蓉蟹，將其蓋到米飯上，據稱由於使用了天津的螃蟹，所以起名叫天津飯。除了這兩種說法以外，還有其他說法提及天津飯的起源，但對於日本為何會有天津飯，直到現在人們仍未弄清原因。<br />\n<br />\n　　報道稱，除了天津飯之外，日本還有名為&ldquo;天津甘栗&rdquo;的糖炒栗子。只要提到炒栗子就是指天津甘栗，已經成為一個品牌。據說，雖然被稱為天津甘栗，但實際上天津並非栗子的產地而是供貨地。日本的進口商&ldquo;東洋軒&rdquo;與河北省青龍、遷西等地栗子種植戶簽署合同，直接採購。這些栗子每年秋季經由天津運到日本，在冷凍狀態下能夠保鮮一年。商戶每天在店裡炒出必要的量，以炒栗子的形式出售。對於天津甘栗的由來，其實很多日本人並不了解。<br />\n<br />\n　　報道稱，天津飯和天津甘栗在日本被視為&ldquo;來自中國的食物&rdquo;，非常有名，但幾乎沒有日本人知道其正確的由來，也很少有人提出疑問。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.crntt.com/doc/1051/4/1/5/105141531.html?coluid=0&amp;kindid=0&amp;docid=105141531&amp;mdate=0726100103\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.crntt.com%2Fdoc%2F1051%2F4%2F1%2F5%2F105141531.html%3Fcoluid%3D0%26kindid%3D0%26docid%3D105141531%26mdate%3D0726100103&d=Tv%2Fq8DN9P5syaUAyWEYo3NibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=00d32ac9\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.crntt.com/doc/1051/4/1/5/105141531.html?coluid=0&amp;kindid=0&amp;docid=105141531&amp;mdate=0726100103</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://livedoor.blogimg.jp/conbul/imgs/a/3/a30d268f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Flivedoor.blogimg.jp%2Fconbul%2Fimgs%2Fa%2F3%2Fa30d268f.jpg&h=b225b2fe&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2cd0f46f2cf84a5018dc74739d3ac93ba5f9dadc","tid":756334,"uid":17641,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T03:26:12.000Z","msg":"所以日本是屬於中國的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f9a7027e6bea6a6b800533d8f6f232e8aa1551e","tid":756334,"uid":1637,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T03:28:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/26/112841_7ce39ede8950252ff32754072c793dd4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F26%2F112841_7ce39ede8950252ff32754072c793dd4.png&h=3ef517bc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0451b934ac07f9ce9ea7aca0742e246fd59bae22","tid":756334,"uid":33868,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T03:29:03.000Z","msg":"香港的士飯"},{"pid":"0fb917cfca1104dfa6c46965292b7245d82aa1b7","tid":756334,"uid":33907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T03:53:12.000Z","msg":"天津蘑菇飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 希望快啲再食到"},{"pid":"ddc214687649cc23540b23e02db712d5b8dbeb3d","tid":756334,"uid":8410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T03:57:21.000Z","msg":"芙蓉蛋飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22aec4192e484ad4d8f8e7c6b48deed75ad87ca4","tid":756334,"uid":124537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T04:00:39.000Z","msg":"揚州炒飯 福建炒飯 星州炒米<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b6266027133a70af831ba3aa8d1ec107e8c8a62","tid":756334,"uid":142053,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T04:06:14.000Z","msg":"屌 睇標題以為講緊龍珠嗰個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c96584d7b9d86c05425feceebd5bc81062338d3","tid":756334,"uid":166413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T04:08:55.000Z","msg":"太陽拳‼️‼️"},{"pid":"cc6089c1f25c21160d38fa6cb60d5cd81ad3edc9","tid":756334,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T05:41:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfc6877f124bdc5943e1a44e6170048cfa41e893","tid":756334,"uid":155337,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T05:59:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">新氣功炮</span></span>"},{"pid":"b85054c0b0f98635148b5b7941d432cceb06e2fa","tid":756334,"uid":132405,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T06:03:02.000Z","msg":"想當年天津飯同杜拉格斯55波，去到布歐變垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"388fca44bacf008af822200ecdc01b3679d86e80","tid":756334,"uid":2192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T06:06:27.000Z","msg":"美式米飯王"},{"pid":"12da13f0784a04d044de07bb026ea30bd9276e33","tid":756334,"uid":30478,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T06:13:19.000Z","msg":"show me your love 飯"},{"pid":"07accff3285cf6624e1420fb2924fbd5fdabf6d7","tid":756334,"uid":15826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b85054c0b0f98635148b5b7941d432cceb06e2fa","tid":756334,"uid":132405,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T06:03:02.000Z","msg":"想當年天津飯同杜拉格斯55波，去到布歐變垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T09:27:07.000Z","msg":"幾時有同杜拉挌斯打過?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f7986d104669a061d0bf866582e906